    "Description": "A vulnerability was found in PyTorch 2.6.0. It has been rated as critical. Affected by this issue is the function torch.nn.utils.rnn.unpack_sequence. The manipulation leads to memory corruption. Attacking locally is a requirement. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.\n\nA patch is available through commit [4945180](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/commit/494518046816d29099b7d056a74ffa5c244fdcdd).",
